high_descs: Hang a right to the wall and turn left to face the white round table.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle in the middle of the table next to the loaf of bread.
Slice the red apple in the middle of the table to the right of the head of lettuce.
Put the knife on the table in between the head of lettuce and the loaf of bread on the right side of the table.
Pick up a slice of apple from the middle of the table.
Turn left, hang a left around the edge of the counter and walk to the white stove ahead.
Put the slice of apple inside the microwave above the stove, heat it, remove it and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the black fridge on the left.
Put the heated apple on the top shelf in the middle inside the fridge and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated apple slice in a fridge.

high_descs: Move forward to the middle of the room, turn right, go between the round table and the counter, turn left to face the lettuce on the table.
Pick up the yellow knife on the table.
Slice the apple in the middle of the table into four pieces.
Stick the knife into the table, left of the bread.
Pick up the closest quarter of the apple on the table.
Turn left, move to he middle of the room, turn left, move to the microwave above the stove.
Head the apple piece in the microwave.
Bring the heated apple piece to the fridge to your right.
Put the heated apple piece in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a piece of heated apple in the fridge.
